<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الزُّبُرُ:</span> الكُتُبُ، وَاحِدُهَا زَبُورٌ،<span class="c5"> زَبَرْتُ:</span> كَتَبْتُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>